phrases: Looks like Freeza is out and about, all right.
And so then, right there, I told him...
Wait, hold on now...
What is this?
-What was that!?
-What is going on!?
W- what was that explosion just now?!
V- V- V-
Vegeta!
Damn!
Hey!
Where are the Dragon Balls?
Look at all of you, lined up so loyally!
If you do not want to tell me...
Lousy small fry.
You can swear your allegiance to Freeza from the Other Side now.
Damn it all, Freeza...
Seeing as how Ginyu stayed behind,
the Dragon Balls must be around here somewhere.
In any event, those Earth punks can locate them
with that strange device of theirs.
They should be here very shortly now.
Until then, I will see about changing into some new battle wear.
So, this is what it is like to have a body with a power of 180,000?
However, I think my previous face was more handsome.
Right, Jheese?
Absolutely!
I- I have got to go faster, or Kuririn and Gohan will get killed!
That way?
No, this way!
Ribbit... ribbit... ribbit...
Damn it, I cannot keep my balance very well in this body.
You know, there is something very unusual about the medicine Kakarrot was using.
Not only does it heal injuries,
but it completely restores one's strength as well.
The only ones in my size are the older models, huh?
We are almost there, Kuririn- san!
Kuririn- san, there it is!
G- got it!
So that is their spaceship, huh?
So, you have arrived, Earthlings.
It is no good if they realize I am here.
I have to suppress my battle power, the way they do.
Let us hurry and find them!
No one else seems to be here.
Kuririn- san, wait!
According to the readings on the Radar,
the Dragon Balls are not inside the ship, but away from it.
Where are they, Gohan?
Let us see... this way.
Right over here.
Here they are, Kuririn- san, here!
Yeah, looks like something was buried here, all right.
Why would they put them here?
Okay, let us dig them out!
Right!
Here is one!
I found one!
There is another one over here!
Hooray!
Here is another!
Looks like all seven are here after all!
So that is where they hid them, huh?
We have got them all!
We have got them all!
Good.
Now just summon that Shen Long thing.
l'll put you two away,
and then have my wish of eternal life and youth given to me!
We did it!
Hey, Gohan, what is that on your face?
Well, what about you, Kuririn- san?
Hurry up and summon it, would you!?
We sure worked hard for this, huh?
Yes.
Now Piccolo- san and everyone else can finally be brought back to life.
Do it already!
Summon it!
Okay, here goes.
We have come such a long way for this moment.
Let us have ourselves a look at what the original Shen Long looks like!
Right.
Come forth, Shen Long, and grant me my wish!
Come forth, Shen Long, and grant me my wish!
The incantation is as simple as that?
W - what is wrong?
lsn't something supposed to happen?
What is this Shen Long?
H- h- he is not coming out...
Shen Long is not coming out.
Why not?
Why is not Shen Long blasting out of there?
Maybe the incantation is a little different.
-Shen Long, come forth! - Those dirty punks!
What are they doing?
-Please grant us our wish! - Those dirty punks!
What are they doing?
Maybe his name is not Shen Long.
That is strange.
Kuririn- san, someone is coming this way!
Hey, I can feel two Ki!
Is it those two Ginyu guys?
If so, does that mean that Father was beaten?
Things are turning for the worse again!
They are evil Ki!
There is no mistake,
it has to be those two from before!
W- what happened to Goku, then?
We have got to suppress our own Ki and take cover, Gohan!
Right!
The Dragon Balls have been dug up!
What is going on?
How did anyone know where they were buried?
Goku!
It is me, it is me!
You sure surprised me!
I thought, Ginyu!
It must be that Ginyu guy coming!
I did not know you had beat him,
and convinced his pal to come over to our side.
Are you the one that found the Dragon Balls here?
How did you know where they were?
What are you talking about, Goku?
I used the Dragon Radar to find them, of course.
Radar, did he say?
Damn, they have got something like that?
So, have you gotten your wish granted then?
That is the funny thing.
It did not work.
Shen Long will not appear.
I cannot figure out why.
The password may be different from what we use on Earth.
So, it did not work, huh?
Goku, is something wrong with you?
Something about you...
It just does not seem right.
And how come you are wearing that Scouter, or whatever it is called?
You really want to know?
Kuririn- san!
That is not Father!
Kuririn- san, run!
So, there is another one of you, huh?
I did not get any reading on my Scouter.
Apparently you can control your battle power all the way down to zero.
What do you think you are doing, Goku?!
It is not Father!
That is not Father there!
I- if that is not Goku, then what is going on?
He looks just like him!
I do not know, but I can just tell.
I have switched bodies.
This one was so much stronger, you see.
What!?
H - he is switched bodies?
That is right.
Red Magma of the Ginyu Special Corps, Jheese!
And I am... Commander of the Ginyu Special Corps... Ginyu- sama!
D- damn...
This unfamiliar body makes it hard to read Ki, as well.
Unfamiliar body?
That is right!
If I are not used to this body, he should not be used to my body, either!
You have switched bodies?
That is impossible!
I think I will test it out right now.
The incredible power of a better-than-180,000 battle power!
D- do not do it, Goku!
You are being controlled somehow!
You have been hypnotized or something!
Whether he is actually switched bodies, or has just been hypnotized,
Kakarrot's strength would still be the same.
Things are getting worse and worse!
I am going to keep increasing my power even higher and higher!
I hope you are ready!
Commander Ginyu!
That other bastard followed us here.
What?
I have found you!
You have done well to make it this far.
I should have made the wound more severe.
K- Kuririn, Gohan, listen up!
That are not me!
He is taken over my body!
You mean, it is true?
I- i- it cannot be!
That is Father?
Yahoo!
Yum, yum!
I could not stand that!
That guy is Ginyu!
Do not hesitate to take him down!
There is no way he can defeat you at your present levels!
Go on, start beating on him!
S- start beating on him, you say?
Fool!
You think I cannot defeat them?
This was originally your body!
It is battle power is over 180,000.
There is no reason why that would have changed!
You will see, once you give it a try.
That is my body there.
How do you even expect to use its Ki well, let alone Kaio-ken?
If body and mind are not completely united, you will not get any great power!
Your lies will not work on Ginyu- sama.
I will show you what my battle power is right now!
Jheese...
Yes, sir!
Jheese!
How high is my battle power?
Just how high a battle power does Ginyu have, now that he has stolen Goku's body?
Moreover, will Goku be able to get his own body back?
